          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-green-800 mb-3">What Stitch does</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-green-700">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="shrink-0">&#10003;</span> Generate page designs from text descriptions</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="shrink-0">&#10003;</span> Create design systems (colors, typography, spacing rules)</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="shrink-0">&#10003;</span> Generate design variants of existing screens</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="shrink-0">&#10003;</span> Edit screens within a Stitch project</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="shrink-0">&#10003;</span> Export design references as HTML mockups</li>
            </ul>
