              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="shrink-0">&#10007;</span> Detect bugs or broken content</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="shrink-0">&#10007;</span> Read or modify your codebase</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="shrink-0">&#10007;</span> Fix rendering issues</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="shrink-0">&#10007;</span> Check if images are loading</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="shrink-0">&#10007;</span> Verify data is wired correctly</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-800 mb-2">4-Step Design Workflow</h3>
        <div class="space-y-3 mb-4">
          <div class="bg-stone-50 border-l-4 border-red-700 px-4 py-3 rounded-r">
