          <div class="bg-stone-50 border-l-4 border-red-700 px-4 py-3 rounded-r">
            <p class="font-semibold text-stone-700 text-sm mb-1">2. Stitch generates a full page design</p>
            <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm">Stitch creates the design and auto-generates a design system (colors, typography, component rules).</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-stone-50 border-l-4 border-red-700 px-4 py-3 rounded-r">
            <p class="font-semibold text-stone-700 text-sm mb-1">3. Export design.md</p>
            <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm">Stitch outputs a <code class="bg-stone-100 px-1 rounded">design.md</code> file — keep it in the project root for reference.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-stone-50 border-l-4 border-red-700 px-4 py-3 rounded-r">
